12// Load JSON Wrapper
13#define _QJS_FROM_JSON_F(...) FOR_EACH_2(__FROMJSON_F, __VA_ARGS__)
14#define _QJS_FROM_JSON_B(...) FOR_EACH_2(__FROMJSON_B, __VA_ARGS__)
15#define _QJS_FROM_JSON_BF(option) _QJS_FROM_JSON_##option
16
17// ============================================================================================
18// To JSON Wrapper
19#define _QJS_TO_JSON_F(...) FOR_EACH_2(__TOJSON_F, __VA_ARGS__)
20#define _QJS_TO_JSON_B(...) FOR_EACH_2(__TOJSON_B, __VA_ARGS__)
21#define _QJS_TO_JSON_BF(option) _QJS_TO_JSON_##option

23
24#define __TOJSON_B(base) JsonStructHelper::MergeJson(___json_object_, base::toJson());
25#define __TOJSON_F(name) \
26 if (staticMetaObject.property(staticMetaObject.indexOfProperty(#name)).isRequired() || !name.isDefault()) \
27 { \
28 ___json_object_.insert(#name, JsonStructHelper::Serialize(this->JS_F(name))); \
29 }
30
31#define __FROMJSON_B(name) name::loadJson(___json_object_);
32#define __FROMJSON_F(name) \
33 if (___json_object_.toObject().contains(#name)) \
34 { \
35 JsonStructHelper::Deserialize(this->JS_F(name), ___json_object_.toObject()[#name]); \
36 }

40// ========================================================================================================= Public
41
42#define QJS_FUNC_JSON(CLASS, ...) \
43 public: \
44 QJsonObject toJson() const \
45 { \
46 QJsonObject ___json_object_; \
47 FOR_EACH(_QJS_TO_JSON_BF, __VA_ARGS__); \
48 return ___json_object_; \
49 } \
50 void loadJson(const QJsonValue &___json_object_) \
51 { \
52 FOR_EACH(_QJS_FROM_JSON_BF, __VA_ARGS__); \
53 } \
54 CLASS(const QJsonObject &json) \
55 { \
56 loadJson(json); \
57 }

59// ========================================================================================================= Plain JSON
60#define __TOJSON_PLAIN_F(name) ___json_object_.insert(#name, JsonStructHelper::Serialize(this->name));
61#define __FROMJSON_PLAIN_F(name) \
62 if (___json_object_.toObject().contains(#name)) \
63 JsonStructHelper::Deserialize(this->name, ___json_object_.toObject()[#name]);
64
65#define QJS_PLAIN_JSON(...) \
66 public: \
67 QJsonObject toJson() const \
68 { \
69 QJsonObject ___json_object_; \
70 FOR_EACH(__TOJSON_PLAIN_F, __VA_ARGS__) \
71 return ___json_object_; \
72 } \
73 void loadJson(const QJsonValue &___json_object_) \
74 { \
75 FOR_EACH(__FROMJSON_PLAIN_F, __VA_ARGS__) \
76 }

78namespace QJsonStruct
79{
80 template<typename T>
81 inline void ExternalDeserializer(T &t, const QJsonValue &d)
82 {
83 t.loadJson(d);
84 }
85 template<typename T>
86 inline QJsonValue ExternalSerializer(const T &t)
87 {
88 return t.toJson();
89 }
90} // namespace QJsonStruct

92class JsonStructHelper
93{
94 public:
95 static void MergeJson(QJsonObject &mergeTo, const QJsonObject &mergeIn)
96 {
97 for (const auto &key : mergeIn.keys())
98 mergeTo[key] = mergeIn.value(key);
99 }

101#define LOAD_SIMPLE_FUNC(type, convert_func) \
102 static void Deserialize(type &t, const QJsonValue &d) \
103 { \
104 t = d.convert_func; \
105 }

123 template<typename T>
124 static void Deserialize(QList<T> &t, const QJsonValue &d)
125 {
126 t.clear();
127 for (const auto &val : d.toArray())
128 {
129 T data;
130 Deserialize(data, val);
131 t.push_back(data);
132 }
133 }
134
135 template<typename T>
136 static void Deserialize(QStringList &t, const QJsonValue &d)
137 {
138 t.clear();
139 for (const auto &val : d.toArray())
140 {
141 T data;
142 Deserialize(data, val);
143 t.push_back(data);
144 }
145 }
146
147 template<typename TKey, typename TValue>
148 static void Deserialize(QMap<TKey, TValue> &t, const QJsonValue &d)
149 {
150 t.clear();
151 const auto &jsonObject = d.toObject();
152 TKey keyVal;
153 TValue valueVal;
154 for (const auto &key : jsonObject.keys())
155 {
156 Deserialize(keyVal, key);
157 Deserialize(valueVal, jsonObject.value(key));
158 t.insert(keyVal, valueVal);
159 }
160 }
161
162 template<typename T>
163 static void Deserialize(T &t, const QJsonValue &d)
164 {
165 if constexpr (std::is_enum_v<T>)
166 t = (T) d.toInt();
167 else if constexpr (std::is_same_v<T, QJsonObject>)
168 t = d.toObject();
169 else if constexpr (std::is_same_v<T, QJsonArray>)
170 t = d.toArray();
171 else
172 QJsonStruct::ExternalDeserializer<T>(t, d);
173 }

177#define STORE_SIMPLE_FUNC(type) \
178 static QJsonValue Serialize(const type &t) \
179 { \
180 return { t }; \
181 }

193#define STORE_VARIANT_FUNC(type, func) \
194 static QJsonValue Serialize(const type &t) \
195 { \
196 return QJsonValue::fromVariant(func); \
197 }
198
199 STORE_VARIANT_FUNC(std::string, QString::fromStdString(t))
200 STORE_VARIANT_FUNC(std::wstring, QString::fromStdWString(t))
201 STORE_VARIANT_FUNC(long, QVariant::fromValue<long>(t))
202 STORE_VARIANT_FUNC(unsigned int, QVariant::fromValue<unsigned int>(t))
203 STORE_VARIANT_FUNC(unsigned long, QVariant::fromValue<unsigned long>(t))
204 STORE_VARIANT_FUNC(unsigned long long, QVariant::fromValue<unsigned long long>(t))
205
206#undef STORE_VARIANT_FUNC
207
208 template<typename TValue>
209 static QJsonValue Serialize(const QMap<QString, TValue> &t)
210 {
211 QJsonObject mapObject;
212 for (const auto &key : t.keys())
213 {
214 auto valueVal = Serialize(t.value(key));
215 mapObject.insert(key, valueVal);
216 }
217 return mapObject;
218 }
219
220 template<typename T>
221 static QJsonValue Serialize(const QList<T> &t)
222 {
223 QJsonArray listObject;
224 for (const auto &item : t)
225 {
226 listObject.push_back(Serialize(item));
227 }
228 return listObject;
229 }
230
231 template<typename T>
232 static QJsonValue Serialize(const T &t)
233 {
234 if constexpr (std::is_enum_v<T>)
235 return (int) t;
236 else if constexpr (std::is_same_v<T, QJsonObject> || std::is_same_v<T, QJsonArray>)
237 return t;
238 else
239 return QJsonStruct::ExternalSerializer<T>(t);
240 }
241};
